data.description: $20K IN SELLERS CONCESSIONS, A Chance in your Lifetime to own one of Weatherford's finest old homes, this 1898 Victorian has been lovingly maintained and ready for a new owner. This Regal home sits just two blocks from the historic square and within walking distance to 10 charming restaurants and shopping. The home features two bedrooms downstairs and three upstairs with an office that could be the 6th bedroom. Living room upstairs and downstairs. Bath and a half on each floor. The kitchen has a lot of charm and very spacious with a large pantry. Enjoy the outdoors while relaxing on the back porch and listening to the lovely fountain. Dr. William Mackenzie built this grand Victorian and raised his family there along with his medical practice. Look for the hitching post for the horse on the East side of the sidewalk. Three storage buildings along with a detached 20 x 20 brick garage. Lot is .75 of an acre.25 minutes to downtown Ft Worth,60 minutes to DFW Airport.
